Embedding Layer
│
├── 1. Token Embedding
│     │
│     ├── Vocabulary Embedding Matrix
│     │      ├── Matrix size: (vocab_size × hidden_dim)
│     │      └── Trainable parameters
│     │
│     ├── Token Vector Lookup
│     │      ├── Token ID indexing
│     │      └── Row selection
│     │
│     └── Token Embedding Output
│
├── 2. Positional Information
│     │
│     ├── Positional Encoding Type
│     │      ├── Learned positional embeddings
│     │      ├── Sinusoidal positional encoding
│     │      └── Rotary positional embedding (RoPE)
│     │
│     ├── Position Embedding Matrix
│     │      └── (max_seq_length × hidden_dim)
│     │
│     └── Position Vector Lookup
│
├── 3. Segment / Token-Type Embeddings (optional)
│     ├── Segment embedding matrix
│     ├── Token type lookup
│     └── Segment vector addition
│
├── 4. Embedding Combination
│     ├── Token embedding
│     ├── Positional embedding
│     ├── Segment embedding
│     └── Vector addition
│
├── 5. Embedding Scaling
│     └── Multiply by √hidden_dim
│
├── 6. Embedding Normalization (optional)
│     ├── Layer Normalization
│     └── Parameter scaling
│
├── 7. Embedding Dropout
│     └── Regularization
│
└── 8. Output Hidden State
      └── Passed to Transformer Decoder